OL,3,CCourt of Appeal rejects latest bid to
OL,4,Cblock reopening of Manston Airport
OL,6,FThe Court of Appeal has rejected the
OL,7,Flatest bid by campaigners to block the
OL,8,Freopening of Manston Airport in Kent.
OL,10,FThe judgement issued by Lord Justice
OL,11,FPeter Jackson, Lord Justice Lewis and
OL,12,FLord Justice Warby follows a hearing
OL,13,Fat the Court of Appeal in April.
OL,15,FA bid for a Judicial Review into the
OL,16,Fdecision to give the Manston Airport
OL,17,Fproject the go ahead was dismissed
OL,18,Flast September but objectors then
OL,19,Fappealed that judgement.
