OL,3,CCourt of Appeal rejects latest bid to
OL,4,Cblock reopening of Manston Airport
OL,6,FThe Court's latest judgement means the
OL,7,FDevelopment Consent Order announced by
OL,8,Fthe Department for Transport in August
OL,9,F2022 remains granted and Site owners,
OL,10,FRiverOak Strategic Partners (RSP) can
OL,11,Fnow begin work to recruit staff both
OL,12,Ffor the construction phase and for
OL,13,Foperational roles once the Airport is
OL,14,Fready to reopen.
OL,16,FRiverOak Strategic Partners say they
OL,17,Fcan now move ahead, 'with certainty'
OL,18,Fwith plans to reopen the airport as a
OL,19,Fcargo hub by 2028.
