OL,6,FThe judgement dismisses a crowdfunding
OL,7,Fappeal by Ramsgate resident Jenny
OL,8,FDawes.
OL,10,FMs Dawes said, "We always knew it
OL,11,Fwould be difficult. We may not have
OL,12,Fsucceeded in quashing the second
OL,13,FManston Airport DCO but, importantly,
OL,14,Fthis decision has clarified the rules
OL,15,Fand ensured a modicum of fairness for
OL,16,Ffuture campaigners where the Secretary
OL,17,Fof State relies on new evidence that
OL,18,Fhas not been consulted on when
OL,19,Fredetermining a DCO application.
