OL,6,F"Nothing in the Court of Appeal's
OL,7,Fdecision touches on whether the
OL,8,FSecretary of State was right to
OL,9,Fconclude that evidence based on
OL,10,Finterviews, transcripts of which were
OL,11,Fnot disclosed, was sufficient to
OL,12,Fjustify his decision.
OL,14,F"And nothing in the decision confirms
OL,15,Fthat Manston Airport is viable. The
OL,16,Feconomic case for Manston Airport has
OL,17,Fnot improved, nor have the climate
OL,18,Fchange concerns been resolved.
