OL,6,FI remain firmly of the view that the
OL,7,Fgovernment's decision to proceed with
OL,8,FManston Airport, in the face of all
OL,9,Fthe expert evidence to the contrary
OL,10,Fand the worsening climate change
OL,11,Fcrisis, is nonsensical."
OL,13,FCraig Mackinlay, the Conservative MP
OL,14,Ffor South Thanet, has welcomed the
OL,15,FCourt of Appeal's decision and said:
OL,16,F"I'm delighted with the Court of
OL,17,FAppeal's decision.
